creator: MOONEE PUBLISHING LTD
descriptionHtml:
Looking for tycoon games? Playing business games a lot? Laundry Tycoon – Business Sim is a business simulator game where you run a laundry business. You make money on washing and cleaning clothes. But to succeed in this cleaning game you need to prove yourself as a manager! Grow your business fast to become a business tycoon.

This business simulator game is really easy to play. You are a laundry manager. Simply get dirty clothes from customers and put it in the washing machine. Then take the clean clothes and give it back to get paid. The more clothes you wash the more money you get.

At first, you run the laundry yourself. But then you need help to cope with the influx of customers and their dirty clothes. Thus, in this tycoon simulator you have to do more than in most of the other cleaning games. You need to manage people for success! Get a HR Specialist to hire first workers. This will help you get rid of your laundry routine and focus on your business. Sometimes you will need to contact the HR department to hire new employees and improve your staff’s hard skills.

Indeed, don’t forget to improve your hero skills! Go to the manager desk to increase your speed and upgrade your hero to do the laundry faster. Also, upgrade the speed of the washing machines. Wash more clothes to earn more. Money will help to grow faster to build your own laundry empire. It’s time to become a millionaire tycoon!

WHAT ELSE?

★ Level up your business.
Enlarge your laundry space and buy more washing machines. Build your successful business and leave your competitors behind in Laundry Tycoon business simulator game.

★ Get CEO.
Hire CEO to work with customers and get you rid of the routine. Instead, focus on marketing and profits. Invest more money in advertising to attract more customers. Improve your service quality. This will allow you to rise prices and to become a business tycoon.

★ Serve VIP customers.
Wanna make even more money? Wash clothes for VIPs and get gold for your work. The richer men you attract the faster your business tycoon dream will come true!

Download Laundry Tycoon – Business Sim, pump your laundry business up and become a millionaire tycoon!
